  "title" : "How to preserve insertion order in HashMap?",
  "body" : "<p>I'm using a <code>HashMap</code>. When I iterate over the map, the data is returned in (often the same) random order. But the data was inserted in a specific order, and I need to preserve the insertion order. How can I do this?</p>\n"
